text: Kalinovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Kazangulovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 42 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Davlekanovo, 5 km from Kazangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Kalinovka, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
